Personal Portfolio

This project was developed as part of the Oasis Infobyte Web Development Internship (Level 1). The objective of this project was to create a responsive personal portfolio website that showcases my profile, skills, projects and contact information. While building this portfolio, I focused on creating a clean and modern user interface with a consistent design and smooth user experience.

The website includes a hero section, about section, skills section, projects section and contact section. It is fully responsive and works properly on desktop, tablet and mobile devices. HTML5 was used for the structure, CSS3 for styling and responsiveness, and JavaScript was used to add interactive features.

Through this project, I improved my understanding of responsive web design, layout creation, JavaScript basics and organizing frontend projects.

Technologies Used:
HTML5
CSS3
JavaScript

Developed By:
